text: The Château de Réghat is a château in Maisons-Alfort, Val-de-Marne, Île-de- France, France. ==History== The château was built in the second half of the 18th century and in the 19th century.French Ministry of Culture: Château de Réghat ==Architectural significance== It has been listed as a monument historique since 1979. ==References== Category:Châteaux in Val-de-Marne Category:Monuments historiques of Île-de-France
title: Château de Réghat
